An example reticulation network in evonet format

Source: R/data.R
retnet_evonet.Rd

A small reticulation network for testing purposes.

Usage

retnet_evonet

Format

retnet_evonet

Evolutionary network with 4 reticulations, the base tree has 20 tips and 27 internal nodes:

edge

Edge matrix that describes the base tree toplogy

edge.length

Edge lengths

Nnode

Number of internal nodes

node.label

Labels for internal nodes. Root node: "r"

tip.label

Labels for network tips. (A-D)

root.edge

edge identifier of root

reticulation

Edge matrix for reticulations

ret.length

Reticulation Lengths
